<eesti> - istutamisaasta. </eesti>
<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> The declarations referred to in Article 1 (1) (b) concerning cutting nurseries shall contain at least the following particulars: </inglise>
